{
  "id": "6a086856625132f0b69640d1",
  "title": "アウフヘーベンの逆を言いたい",
  "created": 1778935895,
  "updated": 1778935899,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a086856625132f0b69640d1",
      "text": "アウフヘーベンの逆を言いたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc87a",
      "text": "from [2026/05/16]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc87b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935899
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc87c",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc87d",
      "text": "\tアウフヘーベンの逆を言いたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc87e",
      "text": "\tカレー味のうんことうんこ味のカレー対立からうんこ味のうんこを得るやり方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc87f",
      "text": "\tauf + heben",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc880",
      "text": "\t\tauf: 上に",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc881",
      "text": "\t\theben: 持ち上げる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc882",
      "text": "\t両方反対にしないといけない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc883",
      "text": "\t\tauf",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc884",
      "text": "\t\t\taufstehen (to stand up / get out of bed) ↔ absitzen (to sit down / dismount)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc885",
      "text": "   aufmachen (to put on) ↔ abmachen (to take off)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc886",
      "text": "   aufsetzen (to put on a hat/glasses) ↔ absetzen (to take off)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc887",
      "text": "   aufsteigen (to ascend / get on a bike) ↔ absteigen (to descend / get off) ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc888",
      "text": "   aufgehen (to rise, e.g., the sun) ↔ untergehen (to set)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc889",
      "text": "  heben",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc88a",
      "text": "  \ta. erniedrigen",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc88b",
      "text": "   b. senken ≡ verringern",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc88c",
      "text": "   c. loslassen",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc88d",
      "text": " 音節数的に absenken か untersenken がいいかなー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc88e",
      "text": " verrotten（腐る）とか言う「まさに」な言い回しがある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc88f",
      "text": " \tDer Baumstumpf beginnt zu verrotten. 切り株が腐り始めた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc890",
      "text": " \t発音は /fɛʁˈʁɔtn̩/ ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc891",
      "text": " \t\taufheben が /ˈaʊ̯fˌheːbən/ なので、音節数が足りん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc892",
      "text": " \t\tzu を追加して zu verrotten でいいかも知らん",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc893",
      "text": " \t\t\tツーファロッテン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc894",
      "text": " \t\t\tここからアウフヘーベンは連想しづらい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08685700000000005dc895",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935895,
      "updated": 1778935895
    }
  ]
}